thread.title_full: Ticketebo reviewed by Michelle Campanella (Wanaaring Road Music)

author: Michelle Campanella (Wanaaring Road Music)
title: Michelle Campanella (Wanaaring Road Music)
text: Highly recommend Ticketebo ticket sale platform for your events. The site looks very professional and their fees are lower than other competitors. Staff are very helpful and handle all the setting up of each event at no extra cost.
